SECOND ANNUAL WRMA CONVENTION

    The second Annual Convention of WRMA will be held
 June 7-9, 2000 in Southhampton, Bermuda. It is expected
 to be attended by representatives of over 100 companies
 engaged in weather risk management. The program will
 include informative seminars, speakers, and opportunities
 for networking. On June 8th the program begins early with
 registration, continental breakfast, and end-user panel
 discussions...and more!
www.wrma.org



